    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a Lunar Knight of the Blood Moon, and tonight is your night.  It's time for violence. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Armed with a brutal blade and nimble bow, take the fight to the twisted horrors conjured by the Blood Moon.  Gain experience, grow stronger, and synergize your weapons to crush the enemy forces and survive the night.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This free demo contains introductory levels from the full version of Blood Moon Survivors.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Make heads roll.  Take down punishing bosses with unique combos and abilities.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314000/extras/78a62c47cc1c8a330893d08efa716116.poster.avif?t=1770140539\" width=600 height=367 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314000/extras/78a62c47cc1c8a330893d08efa716116.webm?t=1770140539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >  Master swapping and dual wielding your weapons to mow down hordes of enemies.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314000/extras/4157c2aa24307e1985a3e1c3badbeb88.poster.avif?t=1770140539\" width=600 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314000/extras/4157c2aa24307e1985a3e1c3badbeb88.webm?t=1770140539\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Combine your powers to discover their deadly, evolved forms.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_asse